latestPosts.caption:
Khurumjari mayam, 
Today, I want to share my experiences, challenges, and achievements during my journey in the Mega Miss Northeast 21st Edition. Yes, this is my first time participating in a pageant, and I initially auditioned only because my best friend @pretty_._rk encouraged me to. I had no confidence in myself, but I went ahead just to fulfill her wish.

When I was selected as a finalist, I nervously told my parents, expecting them to disapprove. However, to my surprise, their support was incredible. December felt like a month of endless examinations, and as the new year—2025—began, I found myself at a crossroads. In the first week of January, I felt completely hopeless and considered backing out due to the many challenges I was facing. But my parents and friends gave me the courage, motivation, and support to keep going and give it my best.

I flew back to Manipur on January 10th, and my sister, @kisha_sairem , taught me everything about pageantry—how to carry myself and what it takes to be in a competition like this—all in just one week! Our activities officially began on January 25th, and I am incredibly grateful to @abhijeet_singha_official , and the entire Mega Entertainment team for their constant support and guidance at every step. A special thanks to @abhijeet_singha_official sir, whose words of encouragement have always motivated us. I truly believe that all the contestants, both men and women, have given their best with his support. Not only that I want all the youths out there comes at @mega_entertainment_official 
because this is a place of heaven where everyone is treated equally, accept for who we are and make each one of us unique in our own way.
Most importantly, I am so proud of myself for standing up for myself and making it this far and all I can say is that I’m more excited for what the future holds and if I can learn all these in just 20 days, now I’m more eager to learn more. And yes, @abhijeet sir, we will walk like queens on the 31st and make you proud! Lastly, Thank you eachh one of you all for always supporting and being there for me in every step and I hope that you will support me till the end and after 🥹❤️‍🔥
